With this phrase, Telecinco CEO Paolo Vasile announced his satisfaction at the close of the stock market, the channel he led had increased its value by two times its rival Antena 3.
One aspect, however, dampened his joy: that’s exactly what hurts me; not that we had higher growth, but that we had lower losses, he noted.
